article.description: — Keli Leaupepe had 15 points in Loyola Marymount's 80-59 win over Bellarmine on Friday.
article.headline: Leaupepe scores 15, Loyola Marymount beats Bellarmine 80-59
article.linkText: Leaupepe scores 15, Loyola Marymount beats Bellarmine 80-59
article.story: LOS ANGELES -- — Keli Leaupepe had 15 points in Loyola Marymount's 80-59 win over Bellarmine on Friday. Leaupepe added seven rebounds for the Lions (6-2). Justin Ahrens scored 15 points, going 5 of 12 (4 for 10 from distance). Chance Stephens finished 3 of 6 from 3-point range and 4 for 5 from the line to finish with 13 points. Garrett Tipton finished with 12 points for the Knights (2-4). Bash Wieland added 10 points for Bellarmine. Curt Hopf also had 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
